metadata.name: Hazey Jupyter 1/1
metadata.description:
The view from Washington Street. Travels between portals defy physics hidden in the urbanscape. Recycled flash of 70s glam rock with Nordic summer style. Psychotropical amethyst micromini skirt balanced with amalgams of prints and embroideries. Cotton cream off the shoulder cardigan, strapless burgundy bandage top. Gold chunky chain necklace. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a tanned female model with copper ombre hair, wearing intricate versace styled off the shoulder streetwear white cardigan with pearl buttons and a tight maroon leopard print mini skirt, silver and gold pins and buttons attached to the skirt, silver belly button piercing, walking near the brooklyn bridge in the 2000s in early autumn at midnight, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 85, scale: 11.
